title: Ren & Stimpy Show 06 - Spider-Man vs. Powdered Toast Man
description: So yeah...exactly what it says. This single issue of The Ren & Stimpy Show features a crossover from no less than The Amazing Spider-Man himself. A hilarious issue with some nice easter eggs and callbacks to classic Spidey stories. Also, this issue was written by Dan Slott! Yes, the man currently responsible for the Superior Spider-Man and many other great Spidey stories penned this joke tale. All credit to the original scanners, please seed and enjoy! :-)
